Title: Zombie Atrocity: The Italian Zombie Movie - Part 2
Actors: Jeffrey S. Bromley, Laurie Beckeman, Dan Grams, LaShelle Mikesell
Plot: When his twin brother is brutally murdered, a brave soldier, a sexy psychic, an evil succubus, her oafish boyfriend, two mysterious aliens and the Michigan Militia inadvertently combine forces in a landfill of the living dead.
